<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>지능형 CCTV 분석 시스템 • LLM Pipeline Lab</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Pyodide for running real Python in browser -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/pyodide/v0.26.4/full/pyodide.js"></script>
    <!-- demo.js: 실제 Pyodide 실행 로직 + rich default codes (유지보수용 분리 파일).
        index.html은 UI 구조 + 최소 glue만 담당. demo.js가 로드되면 전역 함수(loadDemoCategory, runPythonViaPyodide 등)를 제공. -->
    <script src="demo.js"></script>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&amp;family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600&amp;display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #6366f1;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', system_ui, sans-serif;
        }
        
        .font-display {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .section-header {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            line-height: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }

        .pipeline-step {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .pipeline-step.active {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            border-color: #6366f1;
        }

        .flow-arrow {
            transition: all 0.5s ease;
        }

        .flow-arrow.active {
            color: #6366f1;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .tech-badge {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            padding: 0.125rem 0.625rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .explanation-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1), 
                       box-shadow 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .explanation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.25);
        }

        .metric {
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        }

        .nav-active {
            color: white;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #6366f1;
        }

        .code-font {
            font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
        }

        .subtle-grid {
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-zinc-200">
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/10 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-xl">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
            <div class="px-8 py-5 flex items-center justify-between">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
                    <!-- Logo -->
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
                        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-white text-2xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tighter">ShadowWatch</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono ml-1">AI</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/5 text-xs font-medium flex items-center gap-x-1.5 border border-white/10">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                        <span class="text-emerald-400 text-xs font-semibold">BiNCS 2026</span>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pyodide Status (B-2) -->
                    <div id="pyodide-status" class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 text-xs text-zinc-400">
                        Pyodide 로딩 대기 중...
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-8 text-sm">
                    <a href="#architecture" class="hover:text-white transition-colors text-zinc-400">아키텍처</a>
                    <a href="#principles" class="hover:text-white transition-colors text-zinc-400">핵심 원리</a>
                    <a href="#demo" class="hover:text-white transition-colors text-zinc-400">인터랙티브 데모</a>
                    <a href="#curriculum" class="hover:text-white transition-colors text-zinc-400">교육 연계</a>
                    
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
                        <a href="https://github.com/samam0234/2026_llm_langchain_mm_rag_fastapi_react_exam.git" 
                           target="_blank"
                           class="flex items-center gap-x-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/20 hover:bg-white/5 transition-all text-sm font-medium">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i>
                            <span>GitHub</span>
                        </a>
                        <button onclick="document.getElementById('detailed-md').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })" 
                                class="px-5 py-2 rounded-2xl bg-white text-zinc-950 font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-zinc-100 transition-all flex items-center gap-x-2">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-lines"></i>
                            <span>상세 설명서</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 pt-16 pb-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-3xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 mb-6">
                <span class="text-emerald-400">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check-double"></i>
                </span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">BiNCS AI·데이터 엔지니어 양성 과정 • LLM 모듈 실습</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="font-display text-7xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tighter font-semibold mb-6">
                지능형 CCTV 보안 분석.<br>
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">LangChain으로 구현하다</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="max-w-xl text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-10">
                OpenCV가 탐지한 객체를 LLM이 실시간으로 분석하고 위험도를 판단합니다.<br>
                LCEL 파이프라인, 메모리, RAG까지 — 실무에서 쓰는 구조를 한눈에 이해하세요.
            </p>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
                <button onclick="document.getElementById('architecture').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' })" 
                        class="group flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-all px-8 h-14 rounded-3xl font-semibold text-lg">
                    <span>파이프라인 구조 보기</span>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                </button>
                
                <button onclick="startSimulation()" 
                        class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 border border-white/30 hover:bg-white/5 transition-all px-8 h-14 rounded-3xl font-semibold text-lg">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play mr-1"></i>
                    <span>시뮬레이션 실행</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-8 mt-10 text-sm text-zinc-500">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400"></i>
                    <span>실제 코드 기반</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400"></i>
                    <span>LCEL + RAG + Memory</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-emerald-400"></i>
                    <span>JSON 구조화 출력</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Problem Statement -->
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 pb-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
            <div class="lg:col-span-5">
                <div class="sticky top-24">
                    <div class="text-indigo-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[3px] mb-3">THE PROBLEM</div>
                    <h2 class="section-header tracking-tight">새벽 2시, 창고에<br>사람이 나타났다.</h2>
                    <p class="mt-6 text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed">
                        단순한 움직임 감지만으로는 부족합니다.<br>
                        "누구인가?", "위험한가?", "과거에 비슷한 사례가 있었나?"<br>
                        까지 판단해야 진짜 보안입니다.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="lg:col-span-7">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="glass rounded-3xl p-6 border border-white/10">
                        <div class="text-red-400 mb-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-exclamation-triangle text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="font-semibold mb-2">기존 방식의 한계</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">단순 알림만 발생 → 운영자 피로 증가, 오탐률 높음</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-3xl p-6 border border-white/10">
                        <div class="text-amber-400 mb-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-brain text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="font-semibold mb-2">LLM의 역할</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">탐지 결과를 문맥 이해 + 위험도 판단 + 조치 제안</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass rounded-3xl p-6 border border-white/10">
                        <div class="text-emerald-400 mb-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-link text-3xl"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="font-semibold mb-2">우리가 만든 해결책</div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">OpenCV + LangChain 파이프라인으로 지능형 판단 시스템 구축</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Architecture Section -->
    <div id="architecture" class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-16 border-t border-white/10 bg-zinc-900/50">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-10">
                <div>
                    <div class="text-indigo-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[3px]">SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE</div>
                    <h2 class="section-header tracking-tight mt-2">전체 파이프라인 구조</h2>
                </div>
                <button onclick="startPipelineAnimation()" 
                        class="flex items-center gap-x-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-sm font-medium transition-all">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-play mr-2"></i>
                    <span>흐름 애니메이션 재생</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Pipeline Visual -->
            <div class="relative">
                <!-- Pipeline Flow -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-6 gap-3 items-center" id="pipeline-container">
                    
                    <!-- Step 1: OpenCV -->
                    <div class="pipeline-step group bg-zinc-900 border border-white/15 rounded-3xl p-5 cursor-pointer" onclick="highlightStep(0)">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-orange-400">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-video text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold">OpenCV / YOLO</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Computer Vision</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">실시간 프레임 분석<br>객체 탐지 (사람, 차량 등)</div>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-[10px] font-mono bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl w-fit">detections: list[dict]</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center">
                        <div class="flow-arrow text-zinc-700 text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2: Formatter -->
                    <div class="pipeline-step group bg-zinc-900 border border-white/15 rounded-3xl p-5 cursor-pointer" onclick="highlightStep(1)">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-sky-400">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-magic text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold">RunnableLambda</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Formatter</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">탐지 결과를<br>프롬프트용 텍스트로 변환</div>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-[10px] font-mono bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl w-fit">format_detections()</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center">
                        <div class="flow-arrow text-zinc-700 text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3: Prompt -->
                    <div class="pipeline-step group bg-zinc-900 border border-white/15 rounded-3xl p-5 cursor-pointer" onclick="highlightStep(2)">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-violet-400">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold">ChatPromptTemplate</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Prompt Engineering</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">시스템 페르소나 +<br>탐지 데이터 주입</div>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-[10px] font-mono bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl w-fit">risk_level | reason | action</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center">
                        <div class="flow-arrow text-zinc-700 text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 4: LLM -->
                    <div class="pipeline-step group bg-zinc-900 border border-white/15 rounded-3xl p-5 cursor-pointer" onclick="highlightStep(3)">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-robot text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold">ChatOpenAI</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">gpt-4o • temperature=0</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">지능적 위험도 판단<br>조치사항 제안</div>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-[10px] font-mono bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl w-fit">JSON 응답 생성</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hidden md:flex justify-center">
                        <div class="flow-arrow text-zinc-700 text-2xl"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 5: Parser + Result -->
                    <div class="pipeline-step group bg-zinc-900 border border-white/15 rounded-3xl p-5 cursor-pointer" onclick="highlightStep(4)">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3 mb-4">
                            <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-2xl bg-rose-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-rose-400">
                                <i class="fa-solid fa-file-export text-xl"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="font-semibold">JsonOutputParser</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-zinc-500">+ Memory</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400">구조화된 dict 반환<br>대화 이력 자동 저장</div>
                        <div class="mt-4 text-[10px] font-mono bg-black/40 px-3 py-1 rounded-xl w-fit">{"risk_level": "위험"}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Status Bar -->
                <div class="mt-8 flex items-center justify-between text-xs px-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-x-2 text-zinc-500">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-1">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-orange-400 rounded-full ring-2 ring-zinc-950"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-sky-400 rounded-full ring-2 ring-zinc-950"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 bg-violet-400 rounded-full ring-2 ring-zinc-950"></div>
                        </div>
                        <span>실시간 파이프라인</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="font-mono text-emerald-400">실행 시간 &lt; 800ms</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Principles -->
    <div id="principles" class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <div class="text-indigo-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[3px]">CORE PRINCIPLES</div>
                <h2 class="section-header tracking-tight mt-3">이 코드가 중요한 이유</h2>
                <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-4 max-w-md mx-auto">단순한 API 호출이 아닌, 실무에서 바로 확장 가능한 구조를 배웁니다.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
                <!-- Principle 1 -->
                <div class="explanation-card glass border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-7 group">
                    <div class="text-indigo-400 mb-5"><i class="fa-solid fa-link text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <div class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">LCEL 파이프라인</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">| 연산자로 각 단계를 독립적으로 연결. 테스트와 유지보수가 쉬워집니다.</div>
                    <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-white/10 text-xs text-zinc-500 font-mono">formatter | prompt | llm | parser</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Principle 2 -->
                <div class="explanation-card glass border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-7 group">
                    <div class="text-violet-400 mb-5"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <div class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">메모리 (Memory)</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">이전 대화와 분석 결과를 기억합니다. 단일 턴이 아닌 연속적인 지능형 대화가 가능해집니다.</div>
                    <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-emerald-400 flex items-center gap-x-1.5">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> 
                        <span>InMemoryChatMessageHistory</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Principle 3 -->
                <div class="explanation-card glass border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-7 group">
                    <div class="text-rose-400 mb-5"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-code text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <div class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">구조화된 출력</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">JSON 강제로 LLM 응답을 항상 예측 가능하게 만듭니다. 프론트엔드 연동이 매우 쉬워집니다.</div>
                    <div class="mt-6 text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded-2xl w-fit font-mono text-rose-300">risk_level | reason | action</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Principle 4 -->
                <div class="explanation-card glass border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-7 group">
                    <div class="text-sky-400 mb-5"><i class="fa-solid fa-database text-3xl"></i></div>
                    <div class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">RAG (검색 증강 생성)</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">과거 탐지 로그를 벡터DB에 저장하고 필요할 때 검색합니다. 환각을 줄이고 사실 기반 판단을 합니다.</div>
                    <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-sky-400 flex items-center gap-x-1.5">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> 
                        <span>ChromaDB + MultiQueryRetriever</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Part Category Navigation -->
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-16 border-t border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-8">
                <div>
                    <div class="text-indigo-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[3px]">LEARNING PATH</div>
                    <h2 class="section-header tracking-tight">Part별 상세 가이드</h2>
                    <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-2">GitHub 레포지토리의 폴더 구조에 맞춰 단계별로 학습하세요.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

